Provides: leechcraft-full
Description: Full LeechCraft installation
 This metapackage installs all main LeechCraft plugins.
 .
 LeechCraft is a free modular "Internet client" application.
 .
 LeechCraft allows one to browse the web, read RSS/Atom feeds, download
 files via BitTorrent, HTTP, FTP and Direct Connect, automatically stream,
 download or play podcasts and other media files and much more.
 .
 Features can be easily added via plugins that can be integrated with
 each other with no effert while staying abstract from the exact
 implementation.

