 download or play podcasts and other media files and much more.

Package: leechcraft-lastfmscrobble
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends},
 leechcraft-core (= ${binary:Version})
Recommends: leechcraft-provider-securestorage
Provides: leechcraft-provider-mediaartistinfo
Description: Last.fm scrobbler for LeechCraft
 This package contains LastFMScrobble, which provides support for various
 Last.FM-related services from scrobbling and streaming to obtaining
 recommendations, similar artists and biographies.
 .
